scripts.text: ... you step into a dense jungle, slumbering under a brilliant blue sky in which several yellow suns are visible. The air here smells different to you, spicier, and the humidity is far more oppressive than the previous Domain; already your clothes feel wet and clingy.

Water drips from the exotic foliage, and beneath your feet tendrils of steam snake upwards from the moist and spongy ground. A colourful bird of some exotic type flutters lazily over you, its raucous cry cutting through the lingering feeling that something is watching you from just behind the jungle's shadow.
